reviewText:
In the next 17 years of my life I would like to make a carttoon surrounded

characters like Heathcliff and Hello Kitty all rolled into one story !

I don't have a anmination story yet on this carttoon idea now but these two carttoons I loved grew up with as a child in the 80's and mid 70's !

To mix my animation idea with a Japanese (Japan) with an American style carttoon someday !
